summary: This mod adds a new house to Skyrim. Its on a floating island over a lake. You can find it by the Lady stone. has its own trader who lives in the islands core.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a new house to Skyrim. Its on a floating island over a lake. You can find it by the lady stone. (1 bed 1 bath) There is a trader in the islands core who has plenty of gold to buy items. Even a doggy! different versions remove parts of the mod to your liking. All luxuries and crafting stations are around neatly and not cluttered. Any bugs or suggestions or feedback, please leave a comment! or rate the mod. updates comming soon! and more mods i hope :D
